                  <condition>
                    <list>
                      <item>
                        <p>Many of the leaves are much stained and torn, especially foll. <locus>5</locus>, <locus>7</locus>, <locus>8</locus>, <locus>17</locus>, <locus>35</locus>, <locus>44</locus>, <locus>45</locus>, <locus>54</locus>, <locus>55</locus>, <locus>58—93</locus> (soaked in oil), <locus>136</locus> and <locus>137</locus>. </p>
                      </item>
                      <item>
                        <p>Of the quires <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘ</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܙ</foreign> are lost, and several others are very imperfect. </p>
                      </item>
                      <item>
                        <p>Leaves are wanting at the beginning, as well as after foll. <locus>8</locus>, <locus>16</locus>, <locus>23</locus>, <locus>55</locus>, <locus>57</locus>, <locus>58</locus>, <locus>78</locus>, <locus>80</locus>, <locus>82</locus> and <locus>83</locus>.</p>
